subclause.text:
identifying
				research and technologies at recipient institutions that have the potential for
				accelerated commercialization;

item.text:
determine which
				projects should receive awards, in accordance with guidelines established under
				subparagraph (C)(ii);

establish
				milestones and associated award amounts for projects that reach
