clause.text:
specific follow-on
				funding identified or obtained, including follow-on funding sources, such as
				Federal sources or private sources;

number of
				projects supported by qualifying institutions receiving a grant under paragraph
				(1) that secure Phase I or Phase II SBIR or STTR awards;

available
				information on revenue, sales or other measures of products that have been
